sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Learner
    participant Frontend as Lovable Frontend
    participant API as FastAPI Backend
    participant Orch as Orchestrator
    participant SessionStore as Session JSON Store
    participant Ingestion as Ingestion Agent
    participant InternalData as Internal Sources JSON
    participant MCP as MCP Integrations Layer
    participant External as External Sources
    participant Planner as Growth Plan Agent

    Learner->>Frontend: Open SkillPilot
    Frontend->>Frontend: Read cached sessionId from browser storage

    alt Returning user session exists
        Frontend->>API: GET /v1/sessions/{sessionId}
        API->>SessionStore: Load persisted session snapshot
        SessionStore-->>API: onboarding state, preferences, sources, progress
        API-->>Frontend: SessionSummary(recommendedRoute=/dashboard)
        Frontend->>API: GET /v1/sessions/{sessionId}/dashboard
        API->>SessionStore: Read dashboard view model
        SessionStore-->>API: next action, XP, streak, growth progress
        API-->>Frontend: DashboardView
    else New user starts onboarding
        Frontend->>API: POST /v1/sessions
        API->>SessionStore: Create local JSON session record
        SessionStore-->>API: sessionId + status=new
        API-->>Frontend: SessionSummary(recommendedRoute=/onboarding)

        Learner->>Frontend: Upload resume or import LinkedIn profile
        Learner->>Frontend: Provide job description and profile fields
        Frontend->>API: POST /v1/sessions/{sessionId}/profile-intake
        API->>Orch: Start profile analysis job
        Orch->>SessionStore: Persist intake payload + job status
        Orch->>Ingestion: Parse resume, JD, and self-reported profile fields
        Ingestion-->>Orch: Extracted skills, likely strengths, missing info
        Orch->>SessionStore: Save draft learner profile
        API-->>Frontend: 202 Accepted(jobId)

        loop Poll profile-analysis job
            Frontend->>API: GET /v1/jobs/{jobId}
            API->>SessionStore: Read job status
            SessionStore-->>API: stage + progressPercent
            API-->>Frontend: JobStatus
        end

        Frontend->>API: GET /v1/sessions/{sessionId}/profile
        API->>SessionStore: Load generated learner profile
        SessionStore-->>API: profile summary + missing-information hints
        API-->>Frontend: ProfileSummary

        Learner->>Frontend: Answer adaptive quiz
        Frontend->>API: POST /v1/sessions/{sessionId}/quiz-responses
        API->>Orch: Refine profile with quiz signals
        Orch->>SessionStore: Update learner profile + onboarding state
        API-->>Frontend: Refined ProfileSummary

        Learner->>Frontend: Enable sources and set preferences
        Frontend->>API: GET /v1/sources/catalog
        API-->>Frontend: Source catalog with mocked internal and live external sources
        Frontend->>API: PUT /v1/sessions/{sessionId}/sources
        API->>SessionStore: Persist enabled sources
        Frontend->>API: PUT /v1/sessions/{sessionId}/preferences
        API->>SessionStore: Persist learning preferences

        Learner->>Frontend: Generate growth plan
        Frontend->>API: POST /v1/sessions/{sessionId}/growth-plan/generate
        API->>Orch: Start growth-plan generation job
        Orch->>SessionStore: Load profile, preferences, enabled sources, current progress
        SessionStore-->>Orch: Session context
        Orch->>Ingestion: Fetch evidence and candidate learning resources

        par Internal sources are mocked
            Ingestion->>InternalData: Read local JSON fixtures
            InternalData-->>Ingestion: Mocked docs, PR feedback, coaching notes
        and External sources are live integrations
            Ingestion->>MCP: Query enabled source connectors
            MCP->>External: Search/fetch YouTube, Google Search, Scholar, Medium, docs
            External-->>MCP: Real results, metadata, and URLs
            MCP-->>Ingestion: Normalized external resources
        end

        Ingestion-->>Orch: Ranked evidence bundle
        Orch->>Planner: Build personalized growth themes, tasks, and rationale
        Planner->>SessionStore: Read historic progress and active goals
        SessionStore-->>Planner: XP, completed tasks, streak, active path
        Planner-->>Orch: Growth plan + task list + next best action
        Orch->>SessionStore: Persist growth plan, dashboard snapshot, task details
        API-->>Frontend: 202 Accepted(jobId)

        loop Poll growth-plan job
            Frontend->>API: GET /v1/jobs/{jobId}
            API->>SessionStore: Read generation status
            SessionStore-->>API: stage + progressPercent
            API-->>Frontend: JobStatus
        end

        Frontend->>API: GET /v1/sessions/{sessionId}/dashboard
        API->>SessionStore: Load dashboard read model
        SessionStore-->>API: next recommended action + progress
        API-->>Frontend: DashboardView
    end

    Learner->>Frontend: Open skill profile, growth path, or task detail
    Frontend->>API: GET /v1/sessions/{sessionId}/skill-profile
    API->>SessionStore: Read skill profile projection
    SessionStore-->>API: strengths, growth areas, role-gap evidence
    API-->>Frontend: SkillProfileView

    Frontend->>API: GET /v1/sessions/{sessionId}/growth-plan
    API->>SessionStore: Read growth plan projection
    SessionStore-->>API: themes, progress, current task
    API-->>Frontend: GrowthPlan

    Frontend->>API: GET /v1/sessions/{sessionId}/tasks/{taskId}
    API->>SessionStore: Read task detail projection
    SessionStore-->>API: rationale, expected outcomes, resources
    API-->>Frontend: TaskDetail

    Learner->>Frontend: Mark task complete
    Frontend->>API: POST /v1/sessions/{sessionId}/tasks/{taskId}/complete
    API->>Orch: Apply progress update
    Orch->>SessionStore: Update task status, XP, streak, and next action
    SessionStore-->>Orch: Updated session snapshot
    Orch-->>API: Task completion outcome
    API-->>Frontend: TaskCompletionResponse
